title.rendered: Day in the Life VLOG (Recipes, BFF Tag, Workout)

content.rendered:
Here is a quick vlog of some of my recipes, having fun with my bestie jessica (which you can check out her channel here: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCjTLvEFCNuCPk6faL-hx6fw )
AND talking about my new guide!:)
Love,
Katie
